Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.70,0:00:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,要对圣母玛利亚保密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.00,0:00:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,预备  开拍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.40,0:00:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,读完这个之后  也就不难理解为何传闻白蔷薇是作者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.90,0:00:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,因为故事舞台怎么看都是莉莉安啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.40,0:00:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,还有  小令也读了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.00,0:00:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,然后她说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.50,0:00:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不要再插手这件事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.10,0:00:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,还说就当没读过这小说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.30,0:00:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,关于传闻的事不想有任何牵扯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.30,0:00:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,CUT OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.50,0:00:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了  由乃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.30,0:00:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,说起来  这附近开了家新的什锦煎饼店你知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.00,0:00:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,咦  什锦煎饼店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.30,0:00:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是听说过  店主是个很风趣的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.70,0:00:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,对对对  叫横山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.40,0:00:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,叫横山啊  你已经去过好几次了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.70,0:00:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,每礼拜都去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.20,0:00:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么不带我去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.10,0:00:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,一煲起电话就停不下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.40,0:00:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,人一直很多  要预约了才能去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.30,0:01:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那今天呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.30,0:01:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,今天  不是说了要预约嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.30,0:01:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那下星期呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.60,0:01:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,下星期没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.80,0:01:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,顺便告诉我哪种好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.30,0:01:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,荞麦面饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.10,0:01:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,荞麦面饭  荞麦面和饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.20,0:01:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,荞麦面和饭
